**Can we go further this year?** What new and exciting ways to interact with this data will we come up with?

* ‚ú® Automatic monthly recap of the latest jurisprudence?
* ‚ö°Ô∏è Dashboard that highlights interesting new trends in the data?
* üí´ Upgrade the SCD Viewer to be 10x better and 100x faster?
* üåü Something else entirely? It's up to you!

